### ValueSet: ParStadiumVS - Expand
# VS URL: https://fhir.cognovis.de/dental/ValueSet/par-stadium
# Expected: expansion.contains has 3 entries
GET http://localhost:8080/ValueSet/par-stadium/$expand
Authorization: Basic basic:secret

### ValueSet: ParStadiumVS - Validate Valid Code (A)
# System: https://fhir.cognovis.de/dental/CodeSystem/par-stadium
