# Actual: result=True
GET http://localhost:8080/ValueSet/$validate-code?url=https://fhir.cognovis.de/dental/ValueSet/par-stadium&system=https://fhir.cognovis.de/dental/CodeSystem/par-stadium&code=A
Authorization: Basic basic:secret

